These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, zucchini
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, video-games
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, zombie
1. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person eating zucchini##8
2. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | lemonade      |
| Food          | zucchini | kiwi    |
| Hobby         | video-games   | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | zombie      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, singing
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, dancer
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, jet-ski
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the mechanic##5
3. the dancer is not to the right of the mechanic##8
4. the person driving the train is not the person who's hobby is singing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | milk        | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks         | singing |
| Job         | dancer | mechanic   |
| Transport   | train               | jet-ski  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, scientific
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, soul
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, british
2 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig
1. the russian is in an odd position##4
2. the british is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
3. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | western       | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | soul    |
| Nationality   | russian | british |
| Pet           | fish        | guinea-pig   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, dancing
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, dressmaker
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, canadian
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the russian is somewhere to the right of the dressmaker##5
2. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking  |
| Job           | dressmaker  | mechanic |
| Nationality   | canadian | russian   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | bike |

